      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "ViMMS 2.0 is a software framework... The simulator framework consists of two core functionalities: the generation of chemicals from multiple sources, and the execution of fragmentation strategies, implemented as controller classes... Controllers are executed in the context of an environment bringing together input chemicals, mass spectrometer and controllers as a single context.",
